---
/**
 * Theme Extensions Gallery
 *
 * Overview of all experimental theme extensions.
 */

import LabLayout from '../../../layouts/LabLayout.astro';
---

<LabLayout
  title="Theme Extensions"
  description="Experimental theme extensions for Vanilla Breeze: motion tokens, backgrounds, fonts, and more."
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/lab/">Lab</a> / <span aria-current="page">Theme Extensions</span>
  </nav>

  <h1>Theme Extensions</h1>
  <p class="lead">
    Exploring new capabilities for the Vanilla Breeze theme system: motion,
    backgrounds, fonts, borders, and more.
  </p>

  <section>
    <h2>Available Extensions</h2>
    <layout-grid data-min="300px" data-gap="m">
      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/motion-tokens/" class="section-card">
        <h3>01. Motion Tokens</h3>
        <p>Expanded motion system with hover effects, transition presets, staggered animations, and View Transitions API integration.</p>
        <layout-cluster data-gap="xs">
          <layout-badge>Hover Effects</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>Stagger</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>View Transitions</layout-badge>
        </layout-cluster>
      </a>

      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/backgrounds/" class="section-card">
        <h3>02. Backgrounds &amp; Surfaces</h3>
        <p>Page and component backgrounds beyond solid colors: gradients, noise textures, glassmorphism, and animated backgrounds.</p>
        <layout-cluster data-gap="xs">
          <layout-badge>Gradients</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>Textures</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>Glassmorphism</layout-badge>
        </layout-cluster>
      </a>

      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/rough-borders/" class="section-card">
        <h3>03. Rough Borders</h3>
        <p>Non-standard border treatments using SVG filters, border-image, mask-image, and CSS techniques for sketchy themes.</p>
        <layout-cluster data-gap="xs">
          <layout-badge>SVG Filters</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>Border Image</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>Mask</layout-badge>
        </layout-cluster>
      </a>

      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/custom-fonts/" class="section-card">
        <h3>04. Custom Fonts</h3>
        <p>External font loading with Google Fonts, variable fonts, display/body pairings, and font loading API patterns.</p>
        <layout-cluster data-gap="xs">
          <layout-badge>Google Fonts</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>Variable Fonts</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>Font Loading</layout-badge>
        </layout-cluster>
      </a>

      <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/sound-effects/" class="section-card">
        <h3>05. Sound Effects</h3>
        <p>Experimental audio feedback using Web Audio API. Click, hover, success, and error sounds with user preference controls.</p>
        <layout-cluster data-gap="xs">
          <layout-badge>Web Audio API</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge data-variant="warning">Experimental</layout-badge>
          <layout-badge>User Prefs</layout-badge>
        </layout-cluster>
      </a>
    </layout-grid>
  </section>
</LabLayout>
